OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWinds easing
OL,6,Fto become mainly light, and while some
OL,7,Flow cloud is likely to spill inland
OL,8,Ffor some places in the east, many
OL,9,Fsouthern and western parts could stay
OL,10,Fcloud-free. Remaining dry throughout.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny cloud clearing through the
OL,13,Fmorning, to give good sunny spells,
OL,14,Falbeit hazy at times. Perhaps a touch
OL,15,Fcooler than recent days, with a light
OL,16,Fnorth to northeasterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
